# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Large pretrained model weights — fetched on demand (see docs/MODELS.md).
# These are third-party, auto-downloadable, and too big to version.
# NOTE: .gitignore has NO inline comments — patterns must be bare on their own line.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# mobileclip_blt.ts  (~572 MB MobileCLIP TorchScript, YOLOE backbone)
mobileclip_blt.ts
# yolov8s-world.pt   (~26 MB YOLO-World open-vocab detector)
yolov8s-world.pt
# yoloe-11s-seg.pt   (~27 MB YOLOE segmentation detector)
yoloe-11s-seg.pt

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Regenerable demo datasets (recreate with `openarm bc-collect ...`).
# The small trained policies (demos/*.pt) ARE versioned so eval runs out-of-box.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
demos/*.npz

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Older upstream OpenArm model trees (~50 MB), kept locally for provenance but
# unused by the code — only v2/ is referenced. Excluded so the public repo ships
# just the active model. Recoverable from docs.openarm.dev. Reversible: delete
# these two lines to publish them.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.3/
v1/

# Video renders (GIF/PNG showcase media IS versioned; raw video is not)
*.mp4
*.gif.tmp

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Internal-only docs: kept locally, not part of the public repo.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
docs/archive/
docs/PUBLISHING_CHECKLIST.md
media/_probe_*.png
03-openarm-control.md
